   func clone():
      return FzSet.new(self)
```

eventually I found that this does not work. should be replaced

```
return FzSet.new(self)
```

 to

```
extends Node
# sub class
class FzSet:
   var st
   func _init(v):
      st = v.st
   func clone():
      return load("res:/fuzzy.gd").FzSet.new(self)
```

But it looks like that scary.

